Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My child, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The story that I'm about to tell you is very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a long, long story of a journey that will be passed down from parent to child endlessly, starting now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you've been saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so slow. Walk faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys know of a menu item called "Ramen Set?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so famished right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.61,0:00:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want more than to eat some Ramen Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.40,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I have no money. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.99,0:00:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! It's the start of a fun puppet show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay after you watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Isn't it great? Isn't it interesting? Isn't it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is this?! What a dirty doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't it do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids are best when they're honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pay me without holding back, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're telling you honestly that it's not cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we'll pay for something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.02,0:01:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.60,0:01:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,R-R-Ramen Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is this person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.34,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you here? Money? I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gooey Concentrated Peach Flavoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're teasing me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This drink is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, the little kids were playing at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.25,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it looked fun, and I wanted to play too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to you as you slept.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been sleeping since yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I poked you, trying to wake you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.44,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but you didn't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so hungry that I couldn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Work? What kind of work?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Puppeteering.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it very important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tool of the trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.05,0:06:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, isn't it? That's enough. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Crow! Crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's the other thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm glad. I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have you been following me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, we're going to play at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to race, throw water at each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the end, we'll say "See you tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...and go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's almost like we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know each other's names yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kamio Misuzu. What's yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm hungry, I have to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I followed her blindly, lured by food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't eating together nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you normally alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.82,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy comes home late, and I don't have a Daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After you're done eating, let's play, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No. If it gets late, I'll have trouble finding a place to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a place to stay yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.07,0:07:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Though I'll probably be sleeping outside anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay at my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we just met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, I'm a person with a dubious background and an unknown history.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you normally let someone like that stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first, your mum won't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's a very sloppy person, so I don't think there'll be any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess I shouldn't be talking about my own mother like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, it's all right if you stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired; I have no energy to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right if we play tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer vacation, so there's plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you think maths will help us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Will quadratic functions be of any use in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why am I helping you with your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your eyes are too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, you sound like Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.75,0:08:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She ran into the shed on her bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It happens all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure it's OK for me to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, I'll convince her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no argument!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can let such a young man stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to stop that bad habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What relationship do you have with Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:16.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\frz1.972\c&H2B2B2B&\pos(463,473)}CLASSMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:16.36,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\frz1.972\c&H2B2B2B&\pos(508,455)}CLASSMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:16.49,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\frz1.972\c&H2B2B2B&\pos(519,453)}CLASSMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:16.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz0.567\pos(553,460)}CLASSMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:16.86,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs72\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz0.26\pos(578,464)}CLASSMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... her classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, you seem to be really old.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:23.91,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs66\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz0.985\pos(447,262)}DON'T FALL FOR ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:24.04,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs66\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz0.985\pos(482,253)}DON'T FALL FOR ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:24.16,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs66\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz0.985\pos(517,242)}DON'T FALL FOR ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:24.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs66\fnThrow My Hands Up in the Air\c&H2B2B2B&\frz359.899\pos(581,222)}DON'T FALL FOR ME
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I would?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to have guts, and I don't dislike that part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Yukito-san is a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. He can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Very serious, not just seriously serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there are two conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll sleep in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll join me in a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, at the end, he said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Perhaps the one who fell in love was me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that! I win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So I replied,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"The fish you don't catch is a mermaid."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that? That struck home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How... did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's at her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, freeloader, why're you looking so stale? Why don't you do something too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My eeeeeyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something? What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be anything, like an erotic confession of love or a hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the doll from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Wow, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making money from this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother also travelled with this vocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no punch line to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good! You're not funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't it great that it's not a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As if that matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I could see the strings, I'd like it better if it were more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He's trying to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter that you don't have that kind of skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just drown the sorrow with some drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Haruko, Kamio Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get another, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you my name so that you wouldn't call me that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such an insensitive man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Are you a runaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you chasing a goal or a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,More so than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite an amusing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I may look like this, but I do think that I have an eye for judging men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can let you stay for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have a favour to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you look after this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen her reckless side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She's impulsive, and if she sees something interesting, she'll be attracted to it like a bee to honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm a babysitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, can you stop her habit of saying that phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,“Gao!” is what she says when she's troubled or about to cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an imitation of a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves dinosaurs, and it's a phrase that she has been using since she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still a child, this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Isn't it summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko left already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she wakes up early every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time in a while that I've eaten breakfast with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, what will you do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll walk you to school. Haruko asked me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She said to watch out so that you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.47,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She still doesn't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done! This is a map of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This map shows where many people congregate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be of use for your work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu-chin is in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to pick you up later. We'll meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,V!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnMareen's Print\c&H43517E&\b1\t(\fscx80\fscy80)\move(225,119,325,184,0,2484)}Japanese use \Nthese, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs25\fnMareen's Print\c&H43517E&\frz27.895\t(\fscx80\fscy80)\move(213,629,315,566,0,2484)}It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\fnMareen's Print\c&H43517E&\t(\fscx80\fscy80)\move(945,697,865,622,0,2484)}Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\fnMareen's Print\c&H43517E&\t(\fscx80\fscy80)\move(534,212,551,255,0,2484)}I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:51.68,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fs27\fnMareen's Print\c&H43517E&\t(\fscx80\fscy80)\move(660,670,650,600,23,2484)}Munch munch
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the world of her heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.11,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you this town's local legendary being?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, if I do it a favour, like in those fairy tales,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it'll give me something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, come over here. I'll show you something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it such a wonderful act that it makes you feel like giving me something in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,PIKO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko! Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko! Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, you evil extraterrestrial creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko... Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:14:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As if I'd let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious extraterrestrial creature stole my doll and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato isn't an extraterrestrial creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.15,0:15:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a wild dog from my neighbourhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing was actually a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko! Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko! Pikopikopiko! Pikori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for the trouble we've caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because Potato took your doll and ran all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, he wanted to play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what he's saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.55,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems there are worlds on the planet that I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you... hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm still keeping that a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kirishima Kano. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kunisaki Yukito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'll name you Freefreeplanetling Number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.38,0:16:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Number 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! And Potato is Number 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.09,0:16:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,\NWhat does a Freefreeplanetling do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,\NThat's the fate of a Freefreeplanetling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Potato, we're free, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go to school now, so we must part here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you a Freefreeplanetling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually believed something like that? You're such a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all the ones wearing that uniform weird or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you ever wondered what you could do if you had magical powers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.59,0:17:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked surprised. See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How was work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, that was a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There won't be business unless it's a place with more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it so quiet even though it's commuting hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this station has already been shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruko told me to warn you whenever you use that phrase.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Tohno-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you panicking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, a great coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Basking in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. It's evening right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tohno Minagi-san, my classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's smart. Her grades are at the top of her class, and she's the president of the Astronomy Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me Tohno as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san... like a leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's hurry and continue blowing bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I'm at my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.63,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that girl your younger sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Minagi's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tohno-san's classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you Minagi's classmate too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an innocent passer-by who was bowled over by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Minagi, this is a perverted serial kidnapper who has come to take Michiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on this side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's a serial kidnapper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,\NNot good! He's excited! Damsel in distress!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it had a great sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san, this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito-san. He's a traveller who is staying at my house right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A traveller?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no hope if you're a perverted serial kidnapper with no place to stay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio-san, we should be leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, I was finally able to make nice bubbles too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep going. Kamikami too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamikami... me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dark soon, so let's do it tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make lunch, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Kamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you should just go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, for tomorrow's lunch, can you make hamburgers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something to that brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I didn't make a single yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When we met yesterday, you were doing the same thing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always turned my thoughts to the sky since I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.05,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that my other self is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that romantic? The thought that the real me is in the sky sounds so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to see so far and with everything on earth seeming insignificant,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd probably feel very gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, that was the beginning of a summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}...as short as a star's twinkle and as long as eternity.
