Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for might be the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cut out to be a parent. I should have stayed alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream. A strange dream about the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a world I'd never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything extends endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, do you have wings in your dreams?
